## External contributions

It's highly recommended and encouraged to contribute to open source projects that we use. Here's some of the things we've done:

- Added [new tag styles to the Design System](https://github.com/alphagov/govuk-frontend/pull/1711)
- Created [GOV.UK Design System community resources](https://github.com/tijmenb/design-system-community-resources) repo
- Improved the [grammar in Design System documentation](https://github.com/alphagov/govuk-design-system/pull/1026)
- Improved the [DfE form builder](https://github.com/DFE-Digital/govuk_design_system_formbuilder)
- Improved the [GOV.UK Notify ruby client](https://github.com/alphagov/notifications-ruby-client/pull/89)
- Improved the [GOV.UK Notify Rails integration](https://github.com/dxw/mail-notify/pull/11)
- Improved the [GOV.UK Rubocop configuration](https://github.com/alphagov/rubocop-govuk/pull/17)
- Improved the [MoJ frontend toolkit](https://github.com/ministryofjustice/moj-frontend/pull/87)
- Improved the [tech docs template docs](https://github.com/alphagov/tdt-documentation/pull/81)
